   <description>
    <narrative xml:lang="EN">Advanced payment to SARC in relation to Q1 expenses. The Syria MPB on March 12th approved to proceed with an advanced payment ahead of the planned GAD to account for the expenses already incurred by the NS as part of the 2021 BRC planned activities. Once the GAD is agreed, it will include reference to this payment and be uploaded to the grant page.
This first tranche of EUR 198,078 covers the following:
- Exit strategy Bayada Centre (January-February)
- Balance payment pilots &#xE2;&#x20AC;&#x2DC;2020&#xE2;&#x20AC;&#x2122;
- Essential running costs o current salaries/per diems January-March
- CVA Lessons learnt workshop April
The supporting documents include:
- Confirmation of approval of advance payment
- Confirmation of balance brought forward from 2020 GAD
- Agreed budget for 2021 activities
- Internal Grant Approval
&#xC2;</narrative>
